Introduction
Nani Studio Limited ("we" or "us" or "our") respects the privacy of our users ("user" or "you"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application Aidesu.

By using Aidesu, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, please do not use Aidesu.

Information We Collect
We may collect information about you in various ways when you use Aidesu. This may include personal information such as your name, email address, and payment information when you subscribe to our premium features, as well as information about your device and usage of Aidesu such as IP address, device type, and operating system.

How We Use Your Information
We may use your information to:

Provide and maintain Aidesu
Improve Aidesu and its features
Respond to your support requests
Process your subscription payment
Monitor usage and performance of Aidesu
Send you promotional offers and other marketing communications
We will never sell or rent your personal information to third parties for their marketing purposes.

How We Share Your Information
We may share your information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as payment processing, customer support, and analytics. We may also disclose your information if required by law or to protect our legal rights.

Data Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Image Uploads

When using Aidesu, users have the option to upload images for various purposes within the application. It is important to clarify that we do not save or store any images uploaded by users. Once an image is uploaded and processed within the application, it is immediately deleted from our servers. We do not retain any copies of the uploaded images, nor do we use them for any other purpose beyond the intended functionality of Aidesu.

Automatic Deletion

To ensure the privacy and security of our users, we have implemented automated processes that delete uploaded images promptly. This means that once an image has been processed and its intended purpose fulfilled, it is automatically removed from our servers without any manual intervention. Our system is designed to prioritize the confidentiality of user data, and this includes the deletion of any uploaded images to minimize the potential for unauthorized access.

Your Responsibility

While we take every precaution to protect your data, users need to exercise caution when uploading images or any other content to Aidesu. We recommend that you only upload images that are appropriate and do not contain sensitive or confidential information. Furthermore, please ensure that you are not violating any copyrights or intellectual property rights when uploading images to Aidesu.

By using Aidesu and uploading images, you acknowledge and understand that you are solely responsible for the content you upload and that Nani Studio Limited bears no liability for any unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such content.

Children's Privacy
Aidesu is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. If you are under 13, please do not use Aidesu or provide any personal information to us.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our information practices. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice in Aidesu.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or Aidesu, please contact us at support@nanistudio.org.

Thank you for using Aidesu!
